---
title: Thai Beef Slaw Bowl with Crushed Peanuts & Coriander
description: Sure, we've been accused of being a little nutty. So what? When the results are as quick and delicious as these
warm pork noodles with plenty of tasty crunch from the crushed peanuts, we'll wear the nutty badge with pride!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
